text: Hsu Chin-te (born 1 February 1966) is a Taiwanese former cyclist. He competed in the individual pursuit event at the 1984 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1966 births Category:Living people Category:Taiwanese male cyclists Category:Olympic cyclists of Taiwan Category:Cyclists at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
